quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  84,1,Igihe Amajuru azo satagurika
  84,2,Nigihe azo tega amatwi arekuriwe n’Umuremyi wayo
  84,3,N’Isi nayo mugihe izo sanzazwa
  84,4,N’ugukura ivyari muriyo igasigara igaragara
  84,5,Igatega amatwi ku Muremyi wayo n’ukwemererwa
  84,6,"Wa muntu we ! mu vy’ukuri wewe urita kurutare kugeza aho muzohura n’Umuremyi wawe, rero ivyo bikorwa vyawe uzobisanga iwe"
  84,7,Nayo uwuzo habwa igitabu ciwe m’ukuboko kwiwe kw’iburyo
  84,8,Rero uyo muntu azo harurwa n’ibiharuro vyoroshe cane
  84,9,"Kandi\tazosubira\tku\tbantu\tbiwe\tmugihe\tazoba\tafise\takanya\tkuneza ntangere"
  84,10,Mugabo uwuzo habwa igitabu ciwe imugongo
  84,11,Uyo muntu azo saba urupfu
  84,12,Kandi azo kwinjira mu muriro udahera
  84,13,Kuko yari afise akanya muneza hamwe n’abiwe
  84,14,Yiketse yuko atazo garuka ku Mana yiwe
  84,15,N’ukubera iki atagarukira Umuremyi wiwe yamye amubona
  84,16,Rero ndarahiye k’ugutukura kw’izuba bugorovye
  84,17,No kw’Ijoro hamwe nivyo ryegeranye
  84,18,No k’Ukwezi mugihe gukwijije imisi yakwo
  84,19,Muzo hura n’ivyabaye hamwe n’ibindi
  84,20,None bafise iki ko batemera
  84,21,Mugihe basomewe iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu ntibayi gamburukira
  84,22,Mugabo bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baguma bahakana gusa
  84,23,N’Imana niyo ifise ubumenyi bwivyo begeranya
  84,24,Rero n’ubabwire ibihano bibabaza cane
  84,25,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana bimwe bivuye k’umitima yabo n’ukugira ibikorwa vyiza, abo nibo bazoba bafise impembo idahera"
  85,1,Ndarahiye ku Majuru afise Inyenyeri
  85,2,No k’umusi w’isango bemerewe
  85,3,N’uwuzoba icabona kuki boneshwa
  85,4,"Barahonejwe\tabantu\tbatoteje\taba\tIsilamu\rbari\tkubirindiro\tvyabo\rvyo\rmubinogo"
  85,5,Bifise umuriro w’inkwi nyinshi cane
  85,6,Mugihe bari bicaye ngaho
  85,7,Nabo bitegereza ivyo bagirirwa abo ba Isilamu
  85,8,"Nabo batara bona inabi iyariyo yose kuri bo, atari ukwemera Imana yabo ariyo nyene intsinzi n’uguhayagizwa bimwe bikwiye"
  85,9,"Ikaba ariyo nyene ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi, n’Imana niyo ibona ibintu vyose"
  85,10,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe batoteza aba Isilamu b’abagabo hamwe naba Isilamu kazi, hanyuma ntibasabe imbabazi, abo bantu bazoronka ibihano vyo mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, kandi bazoronka ibihano biba turira neza cane"
  85,11,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, nukugira ibikorwa vyiza ntankeka bazoronka imirima irimwo inzuzi zica imbere yabo, iyi niyo ntsinzi niniya"
  85,12,Mu vy’ukuri uguhana kw’Umuremyi wawe kurakaze cane
  85,13,Niyo yatanguje kurema ibiremwa vyose naniyo izobagarura
  85,14,"Nayo niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi, n’ugukunda ibiremwa vyayo vyose"
  85,15,Nyene inyegamo y’iteka ntagatifu
  85,16,Umugizi w’ukugira ico yishakiye cose
  85,17,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’ingabo z’abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  85,18,Ariwe Fir’auni hamwe na Thamudu
  85,19,Mugabo abahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri bagumye badadaza gusa
  85,20,N’Imana iraba kikuje kumpande zose
  85,21,Ahubwo iyi ni Qur’ani ntagatifu
  85,22,Kuri urwo rubaho rushinguwe neza
  86,1,Ndarahiye ku Majuru hamwe n’icoza mw’Ijoro
  86,2,None n’igiki kizo kumenyesha ico kintu kizoza mw’Ijoro
  86,3,N’Inyenyeri yaka cane
  86,4,Nta mutima w’Umuntu uwariwe wese atari uko ufise uwuwu cungereye hejuru yiwe
  86,5,"Ahubwo umuntu niyirabe neza, yaremwe mu kintu nyabaki"
  86,6,Yaremwe mumazi asunitswe
  86,7,Avuye hagati y’amagufa y’umugongo n’igikiriza
  86,8,Mu vy’ukuri Imana irafise ubushobozi bw’ukumugarura
  86,9,Umusi hazoserurwa amabanga y’abantu bose
  86,10,Rero nta bushobozi azoba afise canke umufasha
  86,11,Ndarahiye kubicu bizana imvura
  86,12,No kw’Isi isaduka ikazana ibiterwa
  86,13,"Yuko iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, n’imvugo itandukanya ukuri kwama"
  86,14,Kandi si ibijajuro
  86,15,Mu vy’ukuri n’abagira ingeso kuzindi
  86,16,Nanje izo ngeso zabo ndazitereye kure
  86,17,"Nubahe abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, umwanya mutoyi gusa"